00:31:43,737 --> 00:31:46,477
you should stop me.

543
00:31:47,447 --> 00:31:51,097
It's only you who can stop
me when I'm like that.

544
00:31:56,516 --> 00:31:58,526
<i>Dong Suk.</i>

545
00:31:58,527 --> 00:32:03,727
<i>you've gone too far for me to stop you.</i>

546
00:32:03,726 --> 00:32:06,136
What did you want to see me about?

547
00:32:06,136 --> 00:32:08,136
Frankly

548
00:32:08,136 --> 00:32:10,456
I don't have good feelings about you.

549
00:32:10,457 --> 00:32:11,977
About the merchandise
from the big companies

550
00:32:11,976 --> 00:32:15,126
let Hyun Sung Mart sell them again.

551
00:32:17,116 --> 00:32:18,636
Why?

552
00:32:18,636 --> 00:32:21,116
Why should I do that?

553
00:32:31,705 --> 00:32:33,045
When you see this

554
00:32:33,045 --> 00:32:35,935
you may change your attitude toward me.

555
00:32:38,644 --> 00:32:39,834
What is this?

556
00:32:39,834 --> 00:32:42,224
We snuck it out from Hyun Sung.

557
00:32:42,224 --> 00:32:44,534
It's the bid document of Dae Sam.

558
00:32:44,904 --> 00:32:46,624
With what evidence, can
you make such claims?

559
00:32:46,624 --> 00:32:49,404
If you see the bid document
prepared by Hyun Sung

560
00:32:49,404 --> 00:32:51,264
you will know for sure.

561
00:32:51,264 --> 00:32:52,784
Based on your document

562
00:32:52,783 --> 00:32:55,043
they offered a little
more on their terms.

563
00:32:55,043 --> 00:32:57,923
You're trying to cause a dispute
between Hyun Sung and Dae Sam, huh?

564
00:32:57,923 --> 00:32:59,743
You will make that decision.

565
00:32:59,743 --> 00:33:02,373
If you don't want, don't check.

566
00:33:03,293 --> 00:33:06,703
Any evidence this is
not a trick to get me?

567
00:33:06,703 --> 00:33:09,313
If that confirms to be a lie

568
00:33:09,313 --> 00:33:12,243
you can always stop the
merchandise again.

569
00:33:12,243 --> 00:33:13,583
You are in a bind, aren't you?

570
00:33:13,583 --> 00:33:14,603
Are you going to do it or not?

571
00:33:14,603 --> 00:33:17,213
Okay.

572
00:33:18,433 --> 00:33:20,293
By any chance

573
00:33:20,292 --> 00:33:23,402
did you not think I might
go tell on Dong Suk?

574
00:33:24,592 --> 00:33:27,302
That's not who you are.

575
00:33:34,241 --> 00:33:37,091
Kang Dong Suk.

576
00:33:37,092 --> 00:33:39,902
He's more than capable of doing it.

577
00:33:52,301 --> 00:33:55,811
Yes, I understand.

578
00:33:55,811 --> 00:33:57,811
Thank you.

579
00:33:58,840 --> 00:34:04,780
Most big companies contacted
us to send the merchandise to us.

580
00:34:04,810 --> 00:34:06,380
Okay!

581
00:34:06,380 --> 00:34:08,160
We're almost there.

582
00:34:08,160 --> 00:34:10,400
No, we still have a lot
of huddles to overcome.

583
00:34:10,399 --> 00:34:13,429
First, we have to come up
with the revival plan.

584
00:34:13,430 --> 00:34:15,100
- Let's gather around.
- Sure.

585
00:34:15,099 --> 00:34:17,159
This is what I have so far, so...

586
00:34:17,159 --> 00:34:18,669
this may not work.

587
00:34:18,669 --> 00:34:20,839
Wait a sec.

588
00:34:20,839 --> 00:34:25,109
Finally, it looks like
they are starting to work.

589
00:34:25,879 --> 00:34:29,909
You gather all our resources and...

590
00:34:29,909 --> 00:34:32,489
buy as much Hyun Sung stocks.

591
00:34:32,488 --> 00:34:34,808
The price is at the bottom, so...

592
00:34:34,808 --> 00:34:36,668
you should be able to buy them all.

593
00:34:36,668 --> 00:34:38,408
Yes, sir.

594
00:34:39,128 --> 00:34:43,898
Let's now hear people call me
the head of a company.

595
00:34:56,107 --> 00:34:58,437
Weird.

596
00:34:58,437 --> 00:35:01,397
Jin Ah left me because of you.

597
00:35:01,397 --> 00:35:05,247
It was my first time to be
punched by anyone in my life.

598
00:35:05,246 --> 00:35:08,036
There is something about
you that draws me.

599
00:35:08,457 --> 00:35:10,197
Is this what they call
opposite attraction?

600
00:35:10,196 --> 00:35:12,406
I'm not doing this for you.

601
00:35:12,406 --> 00:35:16,036
The person, Kang Dong Suk who
even betrays a friend...

602
00:35:16,036 --> 00:35:18,036
is what I wanted to show you.

603
00:35:18,036 --> 00:35:22,496
Usually, enemy's enemies
become friends.

604
00:35:36,964 --> 00:35:39,394
Are you feeling okay?

605
00:35:39,394 --> 00:35:42,004
Yes, I'm all better.

606
00:35:42,005 --> 00:35:44,695
I just took a few more
days off to just rest.

607
00:35:44,695 --> 00:35:46,555
Please wait a little bit.

608
00:35:46,554 --> 00:35:47,844
It's after rush hour, so...

609
00:35:47,844 --> 00:35:50,334
you should be home soon.

610
00:35:52,025 --> 00:35:55,155
- Mi Ra.
- Yes?

611
00:35:55,154 --> 00:35:58,754
There is a place I want to stop by.

612
00:35:58,754 --> 00:35:59,904
Where?

613
00:35:59,904 --> 00:36:02,334
I want you to come with me too.

614
00:36:02,334 --> 00:36:06,014
She hates me coming, so...

615
00:36:06,014 --> 00:36:08,174
I will use you as an excuse.

616
00:36:08,173 --> 00:36:10,783
Dong Suk will show up soon.

617
00:36:10,783 --> 00:36:13,443
You stay with your heads
down, no matter what.

618
00:36:13,443 --> 00:36:16,523
I will handle it, okay?

619
00:36:17,143 --> 00:36:21,173
Besides, he's not himself right now.

620
00:36:21,173 --> 00:36:24,133
As you already know it,
he's doing something unprofitable.

621
00:36:24,132 --> 00:36:25,522
If he wants to go down,
he should go down by himself.

622
00:36:25,522 --> 00:36:28,082
Why is he bringing us all to it?

623
00:36:28,082 --> 00:36:30,082
Don't you think?

624
00:36:30,082 --> 00:36:33,132
Mi Ra was asking about you, so...

625
00:36:33,132 --> 00:36:34,692
she will be your sister-in-law.

626
00:36:34,692 --> 00:36:38,222
I thought she should know
about your store at least.

627
00:36:38,221 --> 00:36:40,581
Are you really going
to marry my brother?

628
00:36:40,581 --> 00:36:42,891
Of course, our families have
already been introduced.

629
00:36:42,891 --> 00:36:45,031
I was sad that you missed it.

630
00:36:45,031 --> 00:36:47,421
Mi Ra, make sure you marry my brother.

631
00:36:47,421 --> 00:36:48,341
Okay?

632
00:36:48,341 --> 00:36:49,881
That's what I really want.

633
00:36:49,881 --> 00:36:52,881
He needs someone like you.

634
00:36:53,731 --> 00:36:55,721
Okay.

635
00:36:55,720 --> 00:36:59,220
Jin Ah, can I have a sandwich you make?

636
00:36:59,220 --> 00:37:01,610
I've only been having
hospital food lately.

637
00:37:01,610 --> 00:37:03,900
Now I have a craving for it.

638
00:37:04,390 --> 00:37:06,680
Hospital food?

639
00:37:07,150 --> 00:37:09,390
Do you hate me that much?

640
00:37:09,390 --> 00:37:12,420
Can you sit down, so I can see you?

641
00:37:15,829 --> 00:37:17,859
What was wrong?

642
00:37:17,859 --> 00:37:19,859
It wasn't serious.

643
00:37:19,860 --> 00:37:22,510
I passed out for a
short period of time.

644
00:37:23,229 --> 00:37:25,119
By the way

645
00:37:25,119 --> 00:37:26,509
after I passed out

646
00:37:26,509 --> 00:37:28,279
you were the one I
wanted to see the most.

647
00:37:28,278 --> 00:37:29,448
What are you doing seriously?

648
00:37:29,448 --> 00:37:32,148
I don't want to see you.

649
00:37:32,148 --> 00:37:34,858
Do you like him that much?

650
00:37:34,859 --> 00:37:38,369
so much that you would
leave your parents?

651
00:37:38,368 --> 00:37:40,698
Yes.

652
00:37:41,198 --> 00:37:42,988
Do you?

653
00:37:42,988 --> 00:37:45,478
I might be being punished.

654
00:37:46,448 --> 00:37:51,468
Honestly, I was trying to take
away something precious from him.

655
00:37:51,468 --> 00:37:55,638
That's why he's taking away
something precious to me.

656
00:38:02,947 --> 00:38:04,487
Who started it?

657
00:38:04,487 --> 00:38:06,057
Dong Suk.

658
00:38:06,057 --> 00:38:08,117
It should be enough.

659
00:38:08,117 --> 00:38:08,807
Was it you?

660
00:38:08,807 --> 00:38:10,447
I told them to stop.

661
00:38:10,447 --> 00:38:11,347
What?

662
00:38:11,347 --> 00:38:13,037
We were all fed up.

663
00:38:13,036 --> 00:38:15,426
Business shouldn't be
run based on emotions.

664
00:38:15,426 --> 00:38:17,856
I told you that I'd pay
for all your loss.

665
00:38:17,856 --> 00:38:19,946
We agreed to do it not
for the money, but...

666
00:38:19,946 --> 00:38:22,086
for you.

667
00:38:22,656 --> 00:38:24,546
Dong Suk.

668
00:38:24,545 --> 00:38:26,335
You're our leader.

669
00:38:26,336 --> 00:38:28,766
You're a model that we learn from.

670
00:38:28,766 --> 00:38:32,546
So you don't destroying that image...

671
00:38:32,546 --> 00:38:35,086
this is where it ends.

672
00:38:37,785 --> 00:38:41,365
Do you guys agree to this?

673
00:38:47,635 --> 00:38:49,375
Alright then.

674
00:38:49,374 --> 00:38:51,234
Thank you for your support.

675
00:38:51,235 --> 00:38:53,095
We will stop right here then.

676
00:38:53,094 --> 00:38:57,794
Obviously, you're our leader forever.

677
00:39:06,244 --> 00:39:09,274
Mi Ra brought you home safe, right?

678
00:39:09,273 --> 00:39:11,593
Yes.

679
00:39:13,574 --> 00:39:15,464
Take a few more days to rest.

680
00:39:15,463 --> 00:39:18,453
I will take care of the company.

681
00:39:18,453 --> 00:39:22,973
How is it going with the bidding
for petroleum public corporation?

682
00:39:23,673 --> 00:39:28,293
We received the document from
the Planning Department.

683
00:39:28,292 --> 00:39:29,212
I looked through it and...

684
00:39:29,212 --> 00:39:32,912
it looks like it will
come to us this time.

685
00:39:33,832 --> 00:39:38,132
Since I collapsed

686
00:39:38,132 --> 00:39:41,732
I will step down and appoint
you as the president soon.

687
00:39:42,331 --> 00:39:44,791
If the bidding for petroleum public
corporation comes through

688
00:39:44,791 --> 00:39:47,651
it will be a good excuse
to give you that position.

689
00:39:47,652 --> 00:39:50,332
You will have to recover
from your mistakes too.

690
00:39:50,331 --> 00:39:52,521
All the other bidders
are insignificant.

691
00:39:52,521 --> 00:39:54,521
It comes down to a bidding
between us and Dae Sam.

692
00:39:54,521 --> 00:39:56,081
Against Dae Sam

693
00:39:56,080 --> 00:39:57,740
I'm positive I can win.

694
00:39:57,741 --> 00:39:59,501
Don't underestimate them.

695
00:39:59,501 --> 00:40:00,371
If you fail

696
00:40:00,371 --> 00:40:01,991
not only your position at the company

697
00:40:01,990 --> 00:40:04,800
but also Hyun Sung Energy
will be traumatized.

698
00:40:05,620 --> 00:40:08,730
You know that our company isn't
at the top of our game now, right?

699
00:40:08,731 --> 00:40:12,281
I'm saying that this bidding
will most definitely come to us.

700
00:40:12,280 --> 00:40:14,960
Don't worry.

701
00:40:14,960 --> 00:40:17,820
How is it going with Hyun Sung

702
00:40:17,830 --> 00:40:20,710
Distribution that Ji Hyuk
is in charge of?

703
00:40:20,709 --> 00:40:23,409
I'm paying attention.

704
00:40:23,659 --> 00:40:27,089
I thought about it and...

705
00:40:28,059 --> 00:40:30,079
what if we leave him alone?

706
00:40:30,079 --> 00:40:30,769
Father.

707
00:40:30,769 --> 00:40:32,409
If this deal comes through

708
00:40:32,408 --> 00:40:34,868
it will take care of that as well.

709
00:40:34,868 --> 00:40:37,278
Just let him live.

710
00:40:37,278 --> 00:40:39,468
We will focus on Hyun Sung Energy.

711
00:40:39,468 --> 00:40:43,048
We won't have to waste
our resources there.

712
00:40:43,048 --> 00:40:45,288
I can never do that.

713
00:40:45,288 --> 00:40:47,448
My pride won't allow it.

714
00:40:47,448 --> 00:40:48,618
Your pride?

715
00:40:48,618 --> 00:40:51,328
Apart from my pride

716
00:40:51,328 --> 00:40:54,708
he's like a ticking bomb for us.

717
00:40:57,087 --> 00:40:58,807
Once he gains power

718
00:40:58,808 --> 00:41:00,298
we will explode.

719
00:41:00,298 --> 00:41:02,008
Boom!

720
00:41:02,007 --> 00:41:06,087
He and our family can
never coexist together.

721
00:41:06,087 --> 00:41:08,087
Then what shall we do?

722
00:41:08,087 --> 00:41:10,987
We have to crush him,
so he won't be able to get up again.

723
00:41:10,987 --> 00:41:13,417
Don't you think so, father?

724
00:41:15,006 --> 00:41:17,746
Good night.

725
00:41:27,036 --> 00:41:29,596
When did this begin?

726
00:41:29,596 --> 00:41:32,576
Why is it getting more twisted
as the time goes by?

727
00:41:32,576 --> 00:41:34,916
Damn it.

728
00:41:39,265 --> 00:41:41,405
Did you see your father?

729
00:41:41,406 --> 00:41:43,406
Yes.

730
00:41:49,335 --> 00:41:52,365
What is it? Is everything okay?

731
00:41:53,654 --> 00:41:56,884
I may have underestimated Kim Ji Hyuk.

732
00:41:56,884 --> 00:42:00,294
I've been treating him like
a little bug all this time.

733
00:42:00,714 --> 00:42:04,014
Now I will admit that
he can be my match.

734
00:42:04,464 --> 00:42:06,384
Dong Suk.

735
00:42:06,384 --> 00:42:08,964
He's no match for you.

736
00:42:08,964 --> 00:42:11,274
- Don't worry about him.
- No.

737
00:42:11,273 --> 00:42:12,293
If emotions get in the way

738
00:42:12,293 --> 00:42:13,433
I can't win the battle.

739
00:42:13,433 --> 00:42:16,043
I forgot about that for a while.

740
00:42:16,043 --> 00:42:19,203
Now that I admit that he's my match

741
00:42:19,523 --> 00:42:22,613
I'll have to face him properly.

742
00:42:23,523 --> 00:42:27,303
Not with my emotions,
but with my logic.

743
00:42:29,563 --> 00:42:30,863
Hold on.

744
00:42:30,862 --> 00:42:33,372
Sir.

745
00:42:33,372 --> 00:42:35,932
Isn't this a bit too difficult?

746
00:42:35,932 --> 00:42:36,802
What do you think?

747
00:42:36,802 --> 00:42:37,542
In my opinion

748
00:42:37,572 --> 00:42:39,212
conventional market idea
isn't making sense.

749
00:42:39,212 --> 00:42:40,922
It's going to work.

750
00:42:40,922 --> 00:42:43,362
Trust me.

751
00:42:43,362 --> 00:42:45,222
- I understand.
- Let's go.

752
00:42:45,222 --> 00:42:47,482
Hold on.

753
00:42:47,481 --> 00:42:49,351
President Cho.

754
00:42:49,352 --> 00:42:50,962
I've seen it once.

755
00:42:50,961 --> 00:42:53,101
Because of the committee
of the creditors

756
00:42:53,101 --> 00:42:55,541
I will finish up and
submit it right away.

757
00:42:55,541 --> 00:42:57,901
Yes, sir.

758
00:43:00,381 --> 00:43:02,401
What is it? Does he want
you to do something for him?

759
00:43:02,401 --> 00:43:06,051
I've been going over his
financial management.

760
00:43:06,050 --> 00:43:08,440
It's the least I can do for him.

761
00:43:08,440 --> 00:43:10,250
Let's go.

762
00:43:10,251 --> 00:43:12,251
See you later.

763
00:43:18,330 --> 00:43:21,710
There is something I've been
curious about for some time.

764
00:43:21,710 --> 00:43:23,620
He must hate my family.

765
00:43:23,619 --> 00:43:27,469
How come he doesn't come
ready to fight like he used to?

766
00:43:27,469 --> 00:43:28,789
To have his revenge

767
00:43:28,789 --> 00:43:31,719
why is he focusing on getting
Hyun Sung Distribution back?

768
00:43:31,720 --> 00:43:34,830
It might be because of the compensation
for the people at the market.

769
00:43:34,829 --> 00:43:36,419
He takes Hyun Sung
Distribution back and...

770
00:43:36,419 --> 00:43:39,349
