771
00:43:40,028 --> 00:43:44,428
Partly because he wanted to support the
employees who lost their jobs, right?

772
00:43:44,429 --> 00:43:47,659
Yes, he's most likely to do so.

773
00:43:49,838 --> 00:43:53,468
So when he's alone, he's a punk.

774
00:43:53,468 --> 00:43:55,088
When he's with people

775
00:43:55,088 --> 00:43:57,368
he becomes their leader.

776
00:43:57,368 --> 00:43:58,788
His power comes from...

777
00:43:58,787 --> 00:44:01,617
the people who are with him, huh?

778
00:44:01,618 --> 00:44:04,778
Yes, it seems that way to me too.

779
00:44:06,768 --> 00:44:09,828
The way we take away his power is...

780
00:44:09,827 --> 00:44:14,767
we take his people
away one by one, huh?

781
00:44:15,837 --> 00:44:19,097
His people...

782
00:44:19,787 --> 00:44:22,547
That's all. You may leave.

783
00:44:27,897 --> 00:44:30,777
Kim Ji Hyuk's people...

784
00:44:35,496 --> 00:44:38,256
Excuse me.

785
00:44:38,256 --> 00:44:39,746
Mi Ra.

786
00:44:39,746 --> 00:44:41,936
I'm calling to tell you to be careful.

787
00:44:41,936 --> 00:44:46,956
Kang Dong Suk may start to do
something to the people around you.

788
00:44:46,955 --> 00:44:48,125
What do you mean?

789
00:44:48,125 --> 00:44:49,585
<i>He may use the people around you and...</i>

790
00:44:49,585 --> 00:44:51,705
harm you that way.

791
00:44:51,705 --> 00:44:53,565
<i>He might try to make
them betray you or...</i>

792
00:44:53,565 --> 00:44:55,305
Don't worry.

793
00:44:55,304 --> 00:44:57,544
There are no such people around me.

794
00:44:57,544 --> 00:45:00,424
I'm on my way to the committee now.

795
00:45:00,425 --> 00:45:03,585
- Let's talk later.
- Okay.

796
00:45:07,404 --> 00:45:09,224
With this much preparation

797
00:45:09,224 --> 00:45:10,864
it should go smoothly
without a problem, right?

798
00:45:10,864 --> 00:45:13,544
Well, big companies have started to
sell their merchandise to us, and...

799
00:45:13,544 --> 00:45:16,574
we prepared the plan as
thoroughly as possible.

800
00:45:16,573 --> 00:45:20,333
I'm not too happy about the
project proposal, but...

801
00:45:20,333 --> 00:45:23,433
it shouldn't be a problem if
there isn't any variable.

802
00:45:23,433 --> 00:45:25,273
If there is a problem

803
00:45:25,273 --> 00:45:27,583
They will switch the legal
administrator or...

804
00:45:27,583 --> 00:45:28,853
sell it to a different company.

